{"Q0":"When judging the ones I deemed to be more human, I focused on whether the pattern could reasonably resemble my own and whether it exhibited human nature (e.g. attention to faces). {"Q0":"Perhaps I got them all wrong, but I found it easiest when humans were in the pictures as I think humans attend more to other human faces (especially when placed more forward in the picture / when zoomed in).
